ging, which also validate the usefulness of the\nproposed dataset and approach to boost the development of SOD on 360$^\\circ$\nomnidirectional scenes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Sep 2019 08:33:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-12"}
